cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.MM, cs.RO 

This paper is about video object segmentation, which is a computer vision task. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also proposes a novel attention module, which involves learning and selecting relevant features, indicating a possible fit for cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also mentions real-time performance, which suggests a possible fit for cs.MM (Multimedia) and cs.RO (Robotics).
